name: Webflow Assets
description:
Hey guys! I created some assets for Webflow some graphic elements like the boxes and range inputs. I've also included some icons in three colour options. 

You can download the SVG assets here: https://we.tl/t-stNxWQnd70

Feel free to use responsibly. 

If you would like me to include things like meetup covers, social post templates, etc. so please let me know.

Feedback welcome so please send me a tweet https://twitter.com/riyadhgordon
